// Circular Racing Game
class CircularRacingGame {
    constructor() {
        this.app = null;
        this.gameContainer = null;
        
        // Game state
        this.gameState = 'loading'; // loading, playing, paused, gameOver
        this.isPaused = true;
        this.gameStarted = false;
        
        // Track properties
        this.trackRadius = 250;
        this.trackWidth = 120;
        this.centerX = 400;
        this.centerY = 300;
        
        // Player
        this.player = {
            sprite: null,
            angle: 0,
            speed: 0,
            maxSpeed: 4,
            acceleration: 0.15,
            rotation: 0,
            lap: 0,
            lastCheckpoint: 0,
            stunned: false,
            stunnedTime: 0
        };
        
        // AI opponent
        this.ai = {
            sprite: null,
            angle: Math.PI, // Start opposite to player
            speed: 2.5,
            lap: 0,
            lastCheckpoint: 0
        };
        
        // Game objects
        this.rocks = [];
        this.oils = [];
        this.roadTiles = [];
        
        // Input
        this.keys = {};
        
        // UI references
        this.lapCountElement = document.getElementById('lapCount');
        this.speedValueElement = document.getElementById('speedValue');
        this.gameOverElement = document.getElementById('gameOver');
        this.gameResultElement = document.getElementById('gameResult');
        this.gameMessageElement = document.getElementById('gameMessage');
        this.restartBtn = document.getElementById('restartBtn');
        
        this.init();
    }
    
    async init() {
        // Create PixiJS app
        this.app = new PIXI.Application();
        await this.app.init({ 
            width: 800, 
            height: 600, 
            backgroundColor: 0x2d5a2d
        });
        
        // Add canvas to page
        document.getElementById('gameContainer').appendChild(this.app.view);
        
        // Load assets and setup game
        await this.loadAssets();
        this.setupTrack();
        this.setupCars();
        this.setupObstacles();
        this.setupInput();
        this.setupUI();
        
        // Start game loop
        this.app.ticker.add((delta) => this.gameLoop(delta));
        
        this.gameState = 'paused';
        console.log('Game loaded and paused. Click to start!');
    }
    
    // Helper to load Base64 as texture
    async loadTexture(base64) {
        return new Promise(resolve => {
            const img = new Image();
            img.onload = () => resolve(PIXI.Texture.from(img));
            img.src = base64;
        });
    }
    
    async loadAssets() {
        // Load textures from base64 assets
        this.textures = {
            playerCar: await this.loadTexture(ASSETS['car_blue_2.png']),
            aiCar: await this.loadTexture(ASSETS['car_red_4.png']),
            rock: await this.loadTexture(ASSETS['rock1.png']),
            oil: await this.loadTexture(ASSETS['oil.png']),
            road: await this.loadTexture(ASSETS['road_asphalt03.png']),
            sand: await this.loadTexture(ASSETS['land_sand12.png'])
        };
    }
    
    setupTrack() {
        this.gameContainer = new PIXI.Container();
        this.app.stage.addChild(this.gameContainer);
        
        // Create circular track background
        const trackOuter = new PIXI.Graphics();
        trackOuter.circle(this.centerX, this.centerY, this.trackRadius + this.trackWidth/2);
        trackOuter.fill(0x654321); // Brown for sand/dirt
        this.gameContainer.addChild(trackOuter);
        
        const trackInner = new PIXI.Graphics();
        trackInner.circle(this.centerX, this.centerY, this.trackRadius - this.trackWidth/2);
        trackInner.fill(0x333333); // Dark road
        this.gameContainer.addChild(trackInner);
        
        // Add road tiles for texture
        const numTiles = 32;
        for (let i = 0; i < numTiles; i++) {
            const angle = (i / numTiles) * Math.PI * 2;
            const x = this.centerX + Math.cos(angle) * this.trackRadius;
            const y = this.centerY + Math.sin(angle) * this.trackRadius;
            
            const roadTile = new PIXI.Sprite(this.textures.road);
            roadTile.anchor.set(0.5);
            roadTile.x = x;
            roadTile.y = y;
            roadTile.rotation = angle + Math.PI/2;
            roadTile.scale.set(0.8);
            roadTile.alpha = 0.3;
            this.gameContainer.addChild(roadTile);
        }
        
        // Add finish line at the top of the track (12 o'clock position)
        const finishLine = new PIXI.Graphics();
        finishLine.rect(this.centerX - (this.trackWidth + 10)/2, this.centerY - this.trackRadius - 2, this.trackWidth + 10, 4);
        finishLine.fill(0xFFFFFF);
        this.gameContainer.addChild(finishLine);
    }
    
    setupCars() {
        // Player car (BLUE)
        this.player.sprite = new PIXI.Sprite(this.textures.playerCar);
        this.player.sprite.anchor.set(0.5);
        this.player.sprite.scale.set(0.7);
        this.player.sprite.tint = 0x0066FF; // Bright blue for player car
        this.updateCarPosition(this.player);
        this.gameContainer.addChild(this.player.sprite);
        
        // AI car (RED)
        this.ai.sprite = new PIXI.Sprite(this.textures.aiCar);
        this.ai.sprite.anchor.set(0.5);
        this.ai.sprite.scale.set(0.7);
        this.ai.sprite.tint = 0xFF0000; // Bright red for AI car
        this.updateCarPosition(this.ai);
        this.gameContainer.addChild(this.ai.sprite);
    }
    
    setupObstacles() {
        // Place rocks on track - AVOID the starting areas
        const numRocks = 6;
        const startingZone = Math.PI / 3; // 60 degree zone around start positions
        
        for (let i = 0; i < numRocks; i++) {
            let angle, validPosition;
            let attempts = 0;
            
            do {
                angle = Math.random() * Math.PI * 2;
                // Check if angle is in safe starting zones
                const distFromPlayerStart = Math.min(Math.abs(angle), Math.PI * 2 - Math.abs(angle));
                const distFromAIStart = Math.min(Math.abs(angle - Math.PI), Math.abs(angle - Math.PI + Math.PI * 2), Math.abs(angle - Math.PI - Math.PI * 2));
                
                validPosition = distFromPlayerStart > startingZone / 2 && distFromAIStart > startingZone / 2;
                attempts++;
            } while (!validPosition && attempts < 20);
            
            const radiusOffset = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 80; // Increase spread
            const x = this.centerX + Math.cos(angle) * (this.trackRadius + radiusOffset);
            const y = this.centerY + Math.sin(angle) * (this.trackRadius + radiusOffset);
            
            const rock = new PIXI.Sprite(this.textures.rock);
            rock.anchor.set(0.5);
            rock.x = x;
            rock.y = y;
            rock.scale.set(0.6); // Make rocks slightly smaller
            this.rocks.push(rock);
            this.gameContainer.addChild(rock);
        }
        
        // Place oil spills - also avoid starting areas
        const numOils = 4;
        for (let i = 0; i < numOils; i++) {
            let angle, validPosition;
            let attempts = 0;
            
            do {
                angle = Math.random() * Math.PI * 2;
                const distFromPlayerStart = Math.min(Math.abs(angle), Math.PI * 2 - Math.abs(angle));
                const distFromAIStart = Math.min(Math.abs(angle - Math.PI), Math.abs(angle - Math.PI + Math.PI * 2), Math.abs(angle - Math.PI - Math.PI * 2));
                
                validPosition = distFromPlayerStart > startingZone / 3 && distFromAIStart > startingZone / 3;
                attempts++;
            } while (!validPosition && attempts < 20);
            
            const radiusOffset = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 60;
            const x = this.centerX + Math.cos(angle) * (this.trackRadius + radiusOffset);
            const y = this.centerY + Math.sin(angle) * (this.trackRadius + radiusOffset);
            
            const oil = new PIXI.Sprite(this.textures.oil);
            oil.anchor.set(0.5);
            oil.x = x;
            oil.y = y;
            oil.scale.set(0.4); // Make oil smaller
            oil.alpha = 0.8;
            this.oils.push(oil);
            this.gameContainer.addChild(oil);
        }
    }
    
    setupInput() {
        // Keyboard input
        window.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
            this.keys[e.code] = true;
            this.handleFirstInput();
        });
        
        window.addEventListener('keyup', (e) => {
            this.keys[e.code] = false;
        });
        
        // Touch/mouse input for mobile and first interaction
        this.app.view.addEventListener('pointerdown', (e) => {
            this.handleFirstInput();
        });
        
        // Restart button
        this.restartBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            this.restartGame();
        });
    }
    
    handleFirstInput() {
        if (this.isPaused && this.gameState === 'paused') {
            this.isPaused = false;
            this.gameStarted = true;
            this.gameState = 'playing';
            console.log('Game started!');
        }
    }
    
    setupUI() {
        // UI is already set up in HTML
        this.updateUI(); // Initialize UI display
    }
    
    updateCarPosition(car) {
        // Offset angle by -PI/2 so that 0 angle is at the top of the track (12 o'clock position)
        const adjustedAngle = car.angle - Math.PI/2;
        car.sprite.x = this.centerX + Math.cos(adjustedAngle) * this.trackRadius;
        car.sprite.y = this.centerY + Math.sin(adjustedAngle) * this.trackRadius;
        car.sprite.rotation = car.angle;
    }
    
    gameLoop(delta) {
        if (this.gameState !== 'playing' || this.isPaused) return;
        
        this.updatePlayer(delta);
        this.updateAI(delta);
        this.checkCollisions();
        this.checkLaps();
        this.updateUI();
        this.checkWinCondition();
    }
    
    updatePlayer(delta) {
        if (this.player.stunned) {
            this.player.stunnedTime -= delta;
            // Add visual effect for stunned state
            this.player.sprite.alpha = 0.5 + 0.3 * Math.sin(this.player.stunnedTime * 0.2);
            if (this.player.stunnedTime <= 0) {
                this.player.stunned = false;
                this.player.sprite.alpha = 1.0;
            }
            return;
        }
        
        // Handle input
        let accelerating = false;
        let turning = 0;
        
        if (this.keys['ArrowUp'] || this.keys['KeyW']) {
            accelerating = true;
        }
        
        if (this.keys['ArrowLeft'] || this.keys['KeyA']) {
            turning = -1;
        } else if (this.keys['ArrowRight'] || this.keys['KeyD']) {
            turning = 1;
        }
        
        // Update speed - Fix NaN issue by ensuring speed is always a valid number
        if (accelerating) {
            this.player.speed = Math.min(this.player.speed + this.player.acceleration * delta, this.player.maxSpeed);
        } else {
            this.player.speed = Math.max(this.player.speed - this.player.acceleration * 2 * delta, 0);
        }
        
        // Ensure speed is never NaN
        if (isNaN(this.player.speed)) {
            this.player.speed = 0;
        }
        
        // Update angle based on turning and speed
        if (Math.abs(turning) > 0 && this.player.speed > 0) {
            this.player.angle += turning * 0.03 * delta * (this.player.speed / this.player.maxSpeed);
        }
        
        // Move player - only if speed is valid
        if (!isNaN(this.player.speed) && this.player.speed > 0) {
            this.player.angle += this.player.speed * 0.015 * delta;
        }
        
        // Ensure angle stays within reasonable bounds
        if (this.player.angle > Math.PI * 4) {
            this.player.angle -= Math.PI * 2;
        } else if (this.player.angle < -Math.PI * 2) {
            this.player.angle += Math.PI * 2;
        }
        
        this.updateCarPosition(this.player);
    }
    
    updateAI(delta) {
        // Simple AI that follows the track
        this.ai.angle += this.ai.speed * 0.015 * delta;
        
        // Add some variation to AI speed
        if (Math.random() < 0.01) {
            this.ai.speed += (Math.random() - 0.5) * 0.5;
            this.ai.speed = Math.max(2, Math.min(3.5, this.ai.speed));
        }
        
        // Ensure AI angle stays within bounds
        if (this.ai.angle > Math.PI * 4) {
            this.ai.angle -= Math.PI * 2;
        }
        
        this.updateCarPosition(this.ai);
    }
    
    checkCollisions() {
        const playerSprite = this.player.sprite;
        
        // Check collision with rocks
        for (const rock of this.rocks) {
            if (this.checkSpriteCollision(playerSprite, rock)) {
                this.gameOver('crash');
                return;
            }
        }
        
        // Check collision with oil
        for (const oil of this.oils) {
            if (this.checkSpriteCollision(playerSprite, oil)) {
                this.handleOilCollision();
                break; // Only one oil collision per frame
            }
        }
    }
    
    checkSpriteCollision(sprite1, sprite2) {
        const dx = sprite1.x - sprite2.x;
        const dy = sprite1.y - sprite2.y;
        const distance = Math.sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy);
        return distance < 30; // Reduced collision threshold to be more forgiving
    }
    
    handleOilCollision() {
        if (!this.player.stunned) {
            // Spin the car randomly
            const randomRotation = (Math.random() - 0.5) * Math.PI;
            this.player.angle += randomRotation;
            
            // Stun the player briefly
            this.player.stunned = true;
            this.player.stunnedTime = 60; // frames
            
            // Reduce speed
            this.player.speed *= 0.3;
            
            // Ensure speed is still valid
            if (isNaN(this.player.speed)) {
                this.player.speed = 0;
            }
        }
    }
    
    checkLaps() {
        // Simple lap detection based on angle
        const playerLaps = Math.floor(Math.abs(this.player.angle) / (Math.PI * 2));
        const aiLaps = Math.floor(Math.abs(this.ai.angle) / (Math.PI * 2));
        
        if (playerLaps > this.player.lap) {
            this.player.lap = playerLaps;
        }
        
        if (aiLaps > this.ai.lap) {
            this.ai.lap = aiLaps;
        }
    }
    
    checkWinCondition() {
        if (this.player.lap >= 3) {
            this.gameOver('win');
        } else if (this.ai.lap >= 3) {
            this.gameOver('lose');
        }
    }
    
    updateUI() {
        // Fix NaN display issue
        const currentLap = Math.min(this.player.lap + 1, 3);
        const currentSpeed = Math.round((this.player.speed || 0) * 10);
        
        if (this.lapCountElement) {
            this.lapCountElement.textContent = currentLap;
        }
        if (this.speedValueElement) {
            this.speedValueElement.textContent = currentSpeed;
        }
    }
    
    gameOver(result) {
        this.gameState = 'gameOver';
        this.isPaused = true;
        
        switch (result) {
            case 'win':
                this.gameResultElement.textContent = 'Victory!';
                this.gameMessageElement.textContent = 'Congratulations! You won the race!';
                break;
            case 'lose':
                this.gameResultElement.textContent = 'Defeat';
                this.gameMessageElement.textContent = 'AI overtook you. Try again!';
                break;
            case 'crash':
                this.gameResultElement.textContent = 'Crash!';
                this.gameMessageElement.textContent = 'You crashed into a rock. Be more careful!';
                break;
        }
        
        if (this.gameOverElement) {
            this.gameOverElement.classList.remove('hidden');
        }
    }
    
    restartGame() {
        // Reset game state
        this.gameState = 'paused';
        this.isPaused = true;
        this.gameStarted = false;
        
        // Reset player
        this.player.angle = 0;
        this.player.speed = 0;
        this.player.lap = 0;
        this.player.stunned = false;
        this.player.stunnedTime = 0;
        this.player.sprite.alpha = 1.0;
        this.updateCarPosition(this.player);
        
        // Reset AI
        this.ai.angle = Math.PI;
        this.ai.speed = 2.5;
        this.ai.lap = 0;
        this.updateCarPosition(this.ai);
        
        // Hide game over screen
        if (this.gameOverElement) {
            this.gameOverElement.classList.add('hidden');
        }
        
        // Update UI
        this.updateUI();
        
        console.log('Game restarted and paused. Click to start!');
    }
    
    // Test case support
    loadTestCase(data) {
        console.log('Loading test case:', data);
        
        // Load player state
        if (data.playerAngle !== undefined) {
            this.player.angle = data.playerAngle || 0;
        }
        if (data.playerSpeed !== undefined) {
            this.player.speed = data.playerSpeed || 0;
            // Ensure speed is valid
            if (isNaN(this.player.speed)) {
                this.player.speed = 0;
            }
        }
        if (data.playerLap !== undefined) {
            this.player.lap = data.playerLap || 0;
        }
        if (data.playerStunned !== undefined) {
            this.player.stunned = data.playerStunned;
            this.player.stunnedTime = data.playerStunned ? 30 : 0;
            // Apply visual effect immediately for test cases
            if (this.player.stunned) {
                this.player.sprite.alpha = 0.7;
            } else {
                this.player.sprite.alpha = 1.0;
            }
        }
        
        // Load AI state
        if (data.aiAngle !== undefined) {
            this.ai.angle = data.aiAngle || Math.PI;
        }
        if (data.aiSpeed !== undefined) {
            this.ai.speed = data.aiSpeed || 2.5;
        }
        if (data.aiLap !== undefined) {
            this.ai.lap = data.aiLap || 0;
        }
        
        // Update positions
        this.updateCarPosition(this.player);
        this.updateCarPosition(this.ai);
        
        // Set game state
        this.gameState = data.gameState || 'paused';
        this.isPaused = true; // Always pause after loading test case
        
        // Update UI
        this.updateUI();
        
        console.log('Test case loaded and game paused');
    }
}

// Global function for test cases
window.loadTestCase = function(data) {
    if (window.game) {
        window.game.loadTestCase(data);
    }
};

// Initialize game when DOM is loaded
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    window.game = new CircularRacingGame();
});

body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #1a4d1a;
}

#gameContainer {
    position: relative;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
}

#ui {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 100;
}

#gameInfo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    pointer-events: none;
}

#gameInfo div {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

#gameOver {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
    color: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    pointer-events: auto;
    border: 3px solid #fff;
}

#gameOver h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

#gameOver p {
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
}

#restartBtn {
    background: #4CAF50;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    font-size: 16px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.3s;
}

#restartBtn:hover {
    background: #45a049;
}

.hidden {
    display: none;
}

/* Mobile responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    #gameInfo {
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    #gameOver {
        padding: 20px;
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 300px;
    }
    
    #gameOver h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
    }
    
    #gameOver p {
        font-size: 14px;
    }
}
